        {
            "title": "Chiikawa店員親爆大戰黃牛黨內幕 揭黃牛提早大舉入侵原因：連主辦都措手不及｜Juicy叮",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Chiikawa店員親爆大戰黃牛黨內幕 揭黃牛提早大舉入侵原因：連主辦都措手不及｜Juicy叮\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c8f88d69d6581dedfef82b9c6890eb38/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041611151075845.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Chiikawa店員親爆大戰黃牛黨內幕 揭黃牛提早大舉入侵原因：連主辦都措手不及｜Juicy叮</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>Chiikawa海港城官方限定店引發排隊搶購潮，大批黃牛黨湧現的墟冚場面成為焦點，有Chiikawa店員今日凌晨（16日）在網上發表長文，親爆今次大戰黃牛黨的種種內幕。\n\n</p>\n<p>他坦言：「一出到去全個海旁都係黃牛，係多人到得人驚！」「（上面排隊）九成以上都係黃牛！」昨日（15日）主辦方出狠招，用問問題成功踢走大批黃牛黨，他披露了過程中與這些黃牛「鬥智鬥法」的細節；他又透露，今次黃牛「提早大舉入侵」的原因，連主辦方都一度措手不及。\n\n</p><h2>Chiikawa店員親爆大戰黃牛黨內幕 揭黃牛提早大舉入侵原因：連主辦都措手不及↓↓↓↓</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197791/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/faf7a1f52414c5c8e58d28c99d8dac1a/2025-04/1_1_49.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197792/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e1f7c30fc88adb4483453f164936304/2025-04/2_1_44.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197793/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34eb9028a0386aa776e1a642901de8c0/2025-04/3_1_29.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197794/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/87d2502a847ad74f0bbb664b2a75aeb2/2025-04/4_1_20.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197795/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/682e73cbf914a391329f8998e04751f3/2025-04/5_1_8.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview